    <!-- ESC→BACK remap warning -->
    <string name="fn_esc_remap_warning_title">⚠ ESC → BACK remapping detected</string>
    <string name="fn_esc_remap_warning_desc">Android modifier key remapping is ESC → BACK.\n\nThis is incompatible with the default Fn profile (ESC → F1). After remapping, ESC becomes BACK, and Win+Back conflicts with the F1 mapping.\n\nTip: Win+Backspace has the same effect as Back.\n\nSolutions:\n• Create a new keyboard profile (auto-dismiss this warning)\n• Or go to system Settings to restore the default modifier key layout</string>
